---
title: Korma and Mango Chutney Glazed Chicken with Green Beans, Couscous and Tomato Salsa
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Korma and Mango Chutney Glazed Chicken in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220927_R16_W45_UK_QR12203-8_MB_Main_12_low-833d5cbb.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/korma-and-mango-chutney-glazed-chicken-63174befe38ab9aae75f5fc6-0fa4dac9.pdf
servings: 2
author: Anushka Magan
